description:
With the Pollen Club app you can:
- understand what allergens should be feared right now;
- plan your life, thanks to the forecast of the allergenic situation;
- keep a medical diary (well-being, symptoms and medications);
- compare your well-being with the well-being of other users;
- view the archive for the past days;
- observe the plants near you and decipher their flowering stage;
- plan to move to a safe area, avoid areas with a high risk of allergies.

Simple and visual design and real-time data will help you cope with this difficult period.

We welcome your advice to improve our app. Leave comments and send suggestions to feedback@pollen.club

The data and information in the app are unverified model predictions created for scientific purposes only. They are not medical advice. For health decisions, consult your doctor
You can learn more about data sources and restrictions by following the link when you first start the application or in the settings section
